$ CSS: property display and the values table, table-row and table-cell to create tables with divs only

With → development/web/CSS, it is possible to simulate a → development/web/HTML/tags/table[html `<table>`] using the attribute → development/web/CSS/properties/display and the values `table`, `table-row` and `table-cell`:
gh|about-css|/properties/display/table-elements.html||

See the result of this html on → http://htmlpreview.github.io/?https://github.com/ReneNyffenegger/about-css/blob/master/properties/display/table-elements.html[htmlpreview.github.io].
